{"tid":1222943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[恐怖] 郭文貴預言美國換領事中左 爆政治黑幕","createTime":"2019-06-14T14:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T18:19:18.000Z","uid":240369,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa47955a158fa7740efc852088c9da9a1872609","tid":1222943,"uid":240369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:52:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/worldcountrytaiwan/videos/400818903857180/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fworldcountrytaiwan%2Fvideos%2F400818903857180%2F&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=f327c375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/worldcountrytaiwan/videos/400818903857180/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我唔係好睇得明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多政治黑幕<br />\n尼段片琴日出 佢話美國好快換領事 點知今日真係換左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫香港人留意下換左人之後會發生咩事<br />\n美國急換人做野 係因為發現個領事竟然無講過啲黑幕俾美國知<br />\n佢仲話林鄭做左好多衰野唔見得光 所以搞條逃犯條例去拉爆佢大鑊個啲人<br />\n仲話其實過去4年已經有9000個港人俾人拉左上大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府警察都知 不過唔講<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲睇得明分析到佢啲黑幕?<br />\n<br />\nPS 唔知佢係邊個既人 佢係流亡美國既中國富豪 成日知道好多中共啲貪腐醜聞爆啲權貴料"},{"pid":"d07b60e7e62b262e7a987b9b6435b399d763651f","tid":1222943,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:10:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaTvI_atOao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaaTvI_atOao&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=587a0fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaTvI_atOao</a><br />\n<br />\n5月30日已出"},{"pid":"c941fac755172329a0ba23fe769113aa7585dc30","tid":1222943,"uid":60615,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"期滿換人呀"},{"pid":"017197af92331f21dfd272c5708b5b